  03 Mar 2005; Ciaran McCreesh <ciaranm@gentoo.org> fnord-1.2.ebuild,
  fnord-1.5.ebuild, fnord-1.6.ebuild, fnord-1.7.ebuild, fnord-1.8.ebuild:
  Move sys-apps/daemontools -> sys-process/daemontools

  27 Jan 2005; Christian Zoffoli <xmerlin@gentoo.org> fnord-1.8.ebuild:
  fixed bug #61251, now you can choose if you want to compile it with
  dietlibc or something else, added some missing IUSE

  18 Dec 2004; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> fnord-1.8.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc and added ucspi-tcp to RDEPEND.

  02 Oct 2004; Markus Nigbur <pyrania@gentoo.org> fnord-1.7.ebuild,
  fnord-1.8.ebuild:
  S= unneeded. Added IUSE. Made epatch aware.

  05 Sep 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> :
  Fixed ChangeLog header.

  03 Sep 2004; Pieter Van den Abeele <pvdabeel@gentoo.org> fnord-1.8.ebuild:
  Masked fnord-1.8.ebuild stable for ppc

